{"tid":1171915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美中女主播相約越洋激辯貿易戰","createTime":"2019-05-26T05:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T15:18:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"33f83fa793157117305bcb496c51b27781941fa8","tid":1171915,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190526/20687701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190526%2F20687701&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFN5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=dc40a277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190526%2F20687701&h=84f72b4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190526/20687701</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美中女主播相約越洋激辯貿易戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190526/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190526%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=7c92cf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰戰火燒到兩國電視台，兩名女主播相約周四打擂台激辯。中國央視旗下中國環球電視網（CGTN）主播劉欣，因不滿美國霍士電視財經頻道主播Trish Regan宣揚對華「經濟戰」，自拍短片「為國反擊」，Regan其後還擊。短片吸引逾2,000萬人次觀看；兩名女主播更相約本周三晚（香港時間周四上午）越洋進行辯論。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：華駐美大使：大阪G20習特會未定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190526/large/a0803b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190526%2Flarge%2Fa0803b.gif&h=f21dc87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n央視女主播上霍士應戰<br />\n<br />\n事緣5月14日霍士頻道播出Trish Regan對中美貿易戰的評論，她指貿易失衡是美國必須用在中國身上的「武器」；宣稱中國的繁榮是「以美國利益為代價」，責怪中國人從美國「偷走」數十億美元，美國別無選擇唯有對華一戰。霍士頻道政治立場偏向保守，被視為與總統特朗普友善的傳媒。針對Regan的言論，劉欣22日在Twitter的CGTN官號發短片，批評Regan「用詞情緒化、沒有事實依據」。<br />\n<br />\n劉欣指Regan誤讀數據，其稱中國盜竊知識產權令美國每年損失6,000億美元（約4.68萬億港元）說法，只是來自非牟利機構「國家亞洲研究局」2017年的報告，未經核實且數據指「全球」而非單指「中國」。Regan翌日在節目中反擊，表示自己成中國官媒攻擊目標。對劉欣指她「為特朗普的美國發聲」，Regan表示節目中只說她認為「對自己國家正確的言論」。<br />\n<br />\nRegan又在Twitter向劉欣下戰書，兩人最後約定美東時間周三舉行越洋辯論，劉欣將以嘉賓身份出席霍士頻道節目。有中國網民稱「劉欣主播可是首屆全國大學生英語演講比賽冠軍，嚴重期待這場辯論」。但有美國網民則諷刺中國網民要「翻牆」才能瀏覽Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博/Twitter/環球網  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n華駐美大使：大阪G20習特會未定<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n撐港傘運維權人士出獄即「被旅遊」<br />\n<br />\n華駐美大使：大阪G20習特會未定<br />\nWi-Fi聯盟加入制裁 華為用戶拋售手機藍牙或跟隨 料裁員數千人"},{"pid":"3cd17113c85ac6e2128ee7e433e97a6120def5c1","tid":1171915,"uid":192190,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"美女主播 vs 中女主播"},{"pid":"6a95c6ad5f6e210d90f661a95b79c78dcaa4069d","tid":1171915,"uid":227788,"like":17,"dislike":9,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"大陸嗰位淨係學歷已經輸曬。"},{"pid":"569088e45ae02b02f722f70deaa3d69d123edda0","tid":1171915,"uid":511,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3cd17113c85ac6e2128ee7e433e97a6120def5c1","tid":1171915,"uid":192190,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"美女主播 vs 中女主播"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美女主播 vs 支閪錄音雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457933ded8d7de6c5b6411062a13cf24210d55c6","tid":1171915,"uid":63952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"Bitch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81fa91da25b190c0d99640ee884657cbebfcf26","tid":1171915,"uid":52215,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"不如兩個表演磨豆腐好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm